title: Bo Burnham: Make Happy
description: Combining his trademark wit and self-deprecating humor with original music, Bo Burnham offers up his unique twist on life in this stand-up special.

title: Garfunkel and Oates: Trying to be Special
cast: Riki Lindhome, Kate Micucci, Anthony Jeselnik, Steve Agee
description: Garfunkel and Oates put on a surprise-filled show in Seattle in hopes of raising enough money to make their own comedy special.

title: Kygo: Live at the Hollywood Bowl
description: Join Norwegian electronic music superstar Kygo onstage and behind the scenes as he performs at the famed L.A. venue with a bevy of special guests.

title: Reggie Watts: Spatial
description: The comic innovator delivers a surreal set blending experimental songs, jokes about grits, guns and drugs, and other improvised comedy adventures.
